# Facebook Bot Messenger 

Task manager using [Nodejs](https://nodejs.org/) and API.ai

#Installation


1. Make sure you have NodeJS installed. if you don't have it :

- [Download it from nodejs.org](https://nodejs.org)
- [Install it using NVM](https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm)

2. Clone the repositories :

```
git clone https://github.com/karimalik/fb-messenger-bot.git
```

3. Open the project folder:

```
cd fb-messenger-bot
```

4. Install dependencies:

```
pnpm install
```


5. Start a local dev server:

```
pnpm start